## ğŸ” Features

- ğŸ” City search with **autocomplete suggestions**  
- ğŸ“ Get weather using **current geolocation**  
- ğŸ•’ Shows **local time** of the city  
- ğŸŒ¡ï¸ Current temperature, weather icon, description, humidity, wind  
- â³ 5-hour forecast with weather icons  
- ğŸ¨ Clean, responsive UI with blur & neumorphic style  
- ğŸŒ Multi-language support (based on browser language)

